        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How is AgentGG different from ChatGPT or other AI chatbots?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AgentGG is built with privacy as its primary feature. Unlike most AI chatbots, it doesn't train on your data, uses end-to-end encryption, and gives you one-click session deletion. It's designed for professionals who need AI capabilities without compromising sensitive information.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Do I need prior AI experience to use Generative Geniuses?",
