        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Not at all. The platform's course library starts with fundamentals and progressively builds to advanced topics. Whether you're a complete beginner or an experienced user looking to refine your skills, there's a structured path that fits your level.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use AgentGG for team collaboration?",
